{"tid":2430281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"童書大師Dr.Seuss幾十年前所作的六本作品內容被指種族歧視 宣佈停止出版","createTime":"2021-03-02T23:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T04:29:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f0e02c8c6d5b3e31d7ad721ee6184e5db5e0df","tid":2430281,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T23:41:44.000Z","msg":"美國兒童繪本大師蘇斯博士（Dr.Seuss）幾十年前所作的六本作品，因含「政治不正確」漫畫而宣佈停刊。<br />\n<br />\n負責管理蘇斯博士遺作的蘇斯博士企業（Dr. Seuss Enterprises）在美國時間周二，即蘇斯博士誕辰117周年之日，宣佈《And to Think That I Saw It on Mulberry<br />\n<br />\nStreet》、《If I Ran the Zoo》、《McElligot&rsquo;s Pool》、《On Beyond Zebra!》、《Scrambled Eggs Super!》、《The Cat&rsquo;s Quizzer》停止發行，原因是「這幾本書以傷感情的錯誤方式描繪人」。<br />\n<br />\n六本停刊作品於1937至1976年期間面世，有多幅描繪亞裔和黑人的漫畫被批評帶有種族歧視的定型觀念。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G2Mt8ivGAFxobMmQ5_CRF06rnLU=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZBREN6DHKFD5BI4UL7MZGHVBT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG2Mt8ivGAFxobMmQ5_CRF06rnLU%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZBREN6DHKFD5BI4UL7MZGHVBT4.jpg&h=deb92c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在《And To Think That I Saw It on Mulberry Street》中，一幅漫畫將中國男子畫成「矇豬眼」，被認為是種族歧視。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210303/TFVKKPNXMBGYTHZSJWZ7QDTKKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210303%2FTFVKKPNXMBGYTHZSJWZ7QDTKKA%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiukx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=c05e1770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210303%2FTFVKKPNXMBGYTHZSJWZ7QDTKKA%2F&h=25b5e1cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210303/TFVKKPNXMBGYTHZSJWZ7QDTKKA/</a>"},{"pid":"0f313d7a4bac81d5ff550f5cfd6cc08624b02cbc","tid":2430281,"uid":4574,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T23:48:43.000Z","msg":"美版紅衛兵<br />\n<br />\n用今日嘅標準（仲震係錯嘅標準）<br />\n去批評前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4a0f1ed6688b2c4b8f2c5901281e6feb0029c5","tid":2430281,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T23:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美版紅衛兵<br />\n<br />\n用今日嘅標準（仲要係錯嘅標準）<br />\n去批評前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a35c595ac2d3bd021740b99af88037d3c11411c1","tid":2430281,"uid":256837,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CX5Sf6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCX5Sf6M.jpg&h=6573628c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc2e7b78eca74707156b8a02baf94539e9aaed15","tid":2430281,"uid":292987,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:18:06.000Z","msg":"黐咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身個作者畫風就奇形怪狀 唔通佢畫白人畫得好靚仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢畫動物都樣衰過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOwuina.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOwuina.jpg&h=d845f8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認唔認得出呢隻係牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9955ab418773d417d939076e23c3a0c052fd3a","tid":2430281,"uid":344567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:31:35.000Z","msg":"終於有yellow lives matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69be738b7562796576bc3294bd79a25fff8fa13b","tid":2430281,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc2e7b78eca74707156b8a02baf9